1494
00:58:05,614 --> 00:58:08,043
I still don't have a driver's license.

1495
00:58:08,044 --> 00:58:09,213
(1. Solji still doesn't have a driver's license.)

1496
00:58:09,214 --> 00:58:10,283
I hope you will get one.

1497
00:58:10,284 --> 00:58:12,323
I think I've seen you drive.

1498
00:58:12,324 --> 00:58:13,324
Was it a crime?

1499
00:58:13,325 --> 00:58:14,923
- Did you drive without a license?
- I think that's it.

1500
00:58:14,924 --> 00:58:16,454
- I drove without a license?
- Tae Yeon.

1501
00:58:16,524 --> 00:58:19,064
I eat five servings of meat by myself.

1502
00:58:19,324 --> 00:58:20,523
Five servings of meat?

1503
00:58:20,524 --> 00:58:21,693
I think you can do that.

1504
00:58:21,694 --> 00:58:22,893
Tae Yeon is lying.

1505
00:58:22,894 --> 00:58:24,233
Five servings are a lot.

1506
00:58:24,234 --> 00:58:25,734
- That's a lot.
- I think it's true.

1507
00:58:25,834 --> 00:58:28,433
I once caught an octopus as tall as me.

1508
00:58:28,434 --> 00:58:30,103
- That's possible.
- I'm sure she has a photo of it.

1509
00:58:30,104 --> 00:58:31,743
You can find giant octopuses in Goseong.

1510
00:58:31,744 --> 00:58:33,773
- She does "Hometown Report."
- "Hometown Report."

1511
00:58:33,774 --> 00:58:35,073
- Tae Yeon is telling the truth.
- She did it on "Hometown Report."

1512
00:58:35,074 --> 00:58:36,144
- It can be bigger than that.
- Is it possible?

1513
00:58:36,314 --> 00:58:37,973
Let me ask you something, Tae Yeon.

1514
00:58:37,974 --> 00:58:39,284
What kind of meat do you eat?

1515
00:58:39,714 --> 00:58:41,283
- It doesn't matter.
- Whether it's pork or beef?

1516
00:58:41,284 --> 00:58:42,483
- You can eat five servings?
- Yes.

1517
00:58:42,484 --> 00:58:44,053
- She can eat five servings?
- You know...

1518
00:58:44,054 --> 00:58:45,823
- She's the trot scene's Tzuyang.
- I haven't eaten so much with her.

1519
00:58:45,824 --> 00:58:47,083
- Tae Yeon...
- Seriously.

1520
00:58:47,084 --> 00:58:49,553
