- That's right.

1521
00:58:49,554 --> 00:58:51,994
- Perhaps she eats well.
- I bet she has grown taller...

1522
00:58:52,324 --> 00:58:54,493
- because she eats well.
- Aren't five servings too much?

1523
00:58:54,494 --> 00:58:56,163
Five servings can be small...

1524
00:58:56,164 --> 00:58:58,863
- depending on the restaurant.
- That's right.

1525
00:58:58,864 --> 00:59:00,403
- Then...
- You can eat five servings.

1526
00:59:00,404 --> 00:59:01,733
it's perfectly possible since she's...

1527
00:59:01,734 --> 00:59:03,503
- at the age to eat a lot.
- That's right.

1528
00:59:03,504 --> 00:59:04,833
Do you only eat five servings of meat?

1529
00:59:04,834 --> 00:59:05,943
- How about rice and jjigae?
- You said you'd ask only one.

1530
00:59:05,944 --> 00:59:07,973
- I eat them together.
- Do you eat them as well?

1531
00:59:07,974 --> 00:59:10,073
- I think it's possible.
- I eat whatever I want to eat.

1532
00:59:10,074 --> 00:59:12,813
- Sometimes, I eat meat...
- Five servings are too much.

1533
00:59:12,814 --> 00:59:14,843
- with mul naengmyeon...
- Tae Yeon eats well.

1534
00:59:14,844 --> 00:59:17,153
- and doenjang jjigae.
- Listen.

1535
00:59:17,154 --> 00:59:19,983
Then how much ramyeon can you eat?

1536
00:59:19,984 --> 00:59:21,793
- As for ramyeon, - You don't eat it.

1537
00:59:21,794 --> 00:59:23,693
- I eat only 1 or 2 packets.
- Really?

1538
00:59:23,694 --> 00:59:25,093
- "Only 1 or 2 packets?"
- Listen.

1539
00:59:25,094 --> 00:59:26,663
- Simply put, - Five servings of meat?

1540
00:59:26,664 --> 00:59:29,464
- she can eat about 600g of meat.
- About 600g.

1541
00:59:29,734 --> 00:59:31,093
I think Tae Yeon can eat that much.

1542
00:59:31,094 --> 00:59:32,803
- Six hundred grams?
- Yes.

1543
00:59:32,804 --> 00:59:34,203
- Six hundred grams.
- I don't think she can do it.

1544
00:59:34,204 --> 00:59:35,204
- Because.., - How about Solji?

1545
00:59:35,205 --> 00:59:36,633
- As for Solji...
- Okay.

1546
00:59:36,634 --> 00:59:39,644
I bet Solji has a specialized license.

1547
00:59:39,974 --> 00:59:42,013
- That's what I think.
- What?

1548
00:59:42,014 --> 00:59:43,813
- I bet she has a trailer license.
- Me?

1549
00:59:43,814 --> 00:59:45,413
- What?
- Class one license.

1550
00:59:45,414 --> 00:59:47,683
- A forklift license too.
- Am I too tough?

1551
00:59:47,684 --> 00:59:49,013
- An excavator license too.
- That's right.

1552
00:59:49,014 --> 00:59:50,253
- Heavy equipment.
- You have everything.

1553
00:59:50,254 --> 00:59:51,413
- Me?
- I bet that's the twist.

1554
00:59:51,414 --> 00:59:53,354
- That's the twist.
- The trot scene's Kim Byung Man.

1555
00:59:53,724 --> 00:59:54,883
I bet you have all the licenses.

1556
00:59:54,884 --> 00:59:56,793
- You drive a cultivator too.
- But it says you don't have one.

1557
00:59:56,794 --> 00:59:57,993
You drive a cultivator too.

1558
00:59:57,994 --> 00:59:58,994
- Really?
- You can do anything.

1559
00:59:58,995 --> 01:00:01,993
