1564
01:00:09,774 --> 01:00:11,073
It's half and half.

1565
01:00:11,074 --> 01:00:12,543
I did take a test once.

1566
01:00:12,544 --> 01:00:14,873
I failed the test by a small margin once.

1567
01:00:14,874 --> 01:00:16,673
I should've kept taking it,

1568
01:00:16,674 --> 01:00:18,783
- but work came up.
- That's right. It's a hassle.

1569
01:00:18,784 --> 01:00:21,043
My schedule kept changing,

1570
01:00:21,044 --> 01:00:23,983
