1571
01:00:23,984 --> 01:00:26,523
Solji, what's the car of your dream?

1572
01:00:26,524 --> 01:00:27,923
- The car of my dream?
- Yes, the one you want to drive.

1573
01:00:27,924 --> 01:00:29,794
