- My dream car?

1574
01:00:29,954 --> 01:00:32,394
I don't have much interest in cars, so...

1575
01:00:32,994 --> 01:00:33,994
My dream car?

1576
01:00:34,624 --> 01:00:36,463
You wouldn't be interested if you don't have a license.

1577
01:00:36,464 --> 01:00:38,434
