1627
01:02:06,424 --> 01:02:08,183
Two people.

1628
01:02:08,184 --> 01:02:10,753
Who thinks Solji's statement is a lie?

1629
01:02:10,754 --> 01:02:12,364
You have a license.

1630
01:02:12,864 --> 01:02:14,093
