1642
01:02:40,524 --> 01:02:41,883
- See? I was right.
- I...

1643
01:02:41,884 --> 01:02:43,823
- That's right.
- I was right.

1644
01:02:43,824 --> 01:02:45,993
- Listen.
- That one is too weak...

1645
01:02:45,994 --> 01:02:48,193
